		<div class="navigation">
			<div class="alignleft">&laquo; <a href="http://andrewgelman.com/2016/09/11/31151/" rel="prev">Stan wins again!</a></div>
			<div class="alignright"><a href="http://andrewgelman.com/2016/09/12/solving-statistics-problems-using-stan-my-talk-at-the-nyc-chapter-of-the-american-statistical-association/" rel="next">Solving Statistics Problems Using Stan (my talk at the NYC chapter of the American Statistical Association)</a> &raquo;</div>
